{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Clipboard API","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Clipboard_API","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Clipboard_API\">Clipboard API</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Guides</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Interact_with_the_clipboard\">Interact with the clipboard</a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Clipboard\"><code>Clipboard</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/ClipboardEvent\"><code>ClipboardEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/ClipboardItem\"><code>ClipboardItem</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Navigator/clipboard\"><code>Navigator.clipboard</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element/copy_event\"><code>Element</code>: <code>copy</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element/cut_event\"><code>Element</code>: <code>cut</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element/paste_event\"><code>Element</code>: <code>paste</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Window/clipboardchange_event\"><code>Window</code>: <code>clipboardchange</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>Clipboard API</strong>는 클립보드 명령(잘라내기, 복사, 붙여넣기)에 응답하거나 시스템 클립보드에 비동기적으로 접근하고 쓸 수 있는 기능을 제공합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>참고:</strong> 이 API는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">웹 워커</a>에서 사용할 수 <strong>없습니다</strong>. (<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator\"><code>WorkerNavigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>에 노출되지 않음)</p>\n</div>\n<p>Clipboard API는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Document/execCommand\"><code>document.execCommand()</code></a>를 사용한 클립보드 접근을 대체하기 위해 디자인되었습니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"클립보드_접근","title":"클립보드 접근","isH3":false,"content":"<p>시스템 클립보드에 접근할 땐 <code>Clipboard</code> 객체의 인스턴스를 생성하지 않고, 전역 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/clipboard\"><code>Navigator.clipboard</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>를 사용합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clipboard<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">readText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token parameter\">clipText</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\".editor\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerText <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> clipText<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>위의 코드 조각은 클립보드에서 텍스트를 가져와서, <code>editor</code> 클래스를 가진 첫 번째 요소의 콘텐츠 뒤에 추가합니다. <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/readText\"><code>readText()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>는 (<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/read\"><code>read()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>도 마찬가지로) 클립보드의 내용이 텍스트가 아니면 빈 문자열을 반환하므로, 이 코드는 안전합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"인터페이스","title":"인터페이스","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"clipboard\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Clipboard\"><code>Clipboard</code></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>시스템 클립보드에서 텍스트와 데이터를 읽고 쓸 수 있는 인터페이스를 제공합니다. 명세에서는 \"Async Clipboard API\"라고 부릅니다.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"clipboardevent\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/ClipboardEvent\"><code>ClipboardEvent</code></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/cut_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">cut (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/copy_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">copy (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/paste_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">paste (en-US)</a></code> 이벤트처럼 클립보드 조작에 대한 정보를 제공하는 이벤트를 나타냅니다. 명세에서는 \"Clipboard Event API\"라고 부릅니다.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"clipboarditem_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ClipboardItem\"><code>ClipboardItem</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>클립보드 데이터를 읽거나 쓸 때 데이터 형식을 나타낼 수 있습니다.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"명세","id":"명세","isH3":false,"query":"api.Clipboard,api.ClipboardEvent,api.ClipboardItem","specifications":[]}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"브라우저_호환성","title":"브라우저 호환성","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Clipboard","id":"clipboard_2","isH3":true,"query":"api.Clipboard","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Clipboard_API/bcd.json"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ClipboardEvent","id":"clipboardevent_2","isH3":true,"query":"api.ClipboardEvent","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Clipboard_API/bcd-2.json"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ClipboardItem","id":"clipboarditem","isH3":true,"query":"api.ClipboardItem","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Clipboard_API/bcd-3.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"같이_보기","title":"같이 보기","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://async-clipboard-api.glitch.me/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Async Clipboard API 데모 (Glitch)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://web.dev/image-support-for-async-clipboard/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">web.dev의 Async Clipboard API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"클립보드 접근","id":"클립보드_접근"},{"text":"인터페이스","id":"인터페이스"},{"text":"명세","id":"명세"},{"text":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성"},{"text":"같이 보기","id":"같이_보기"}],"summary":"Clipboard API는 클립보드 명령(잘라내기, 복사, 붙여넣기)에 응답하거나 시스템 클립보드에 비동기적으로 접근하고 쓸 수 있는 기능을 제공합니다.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Clipboard API","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"API del portapapeles","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"API Clipboard","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"クリップボード API","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Clipboard API","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Clipboard API","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/clipboard_api","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/clipboard_api/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Clipboard_API","title":"Clipboard API"}],"pageT